@startuml scfca_docker_compose_container_model

title SCFCA PoC — Docker Compose Container Execution Model

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

rectangle "Host" as host {
  node "Developer / CI Runner Host" as hostnode
  rectangle "Published ports" as ports {
    [5432/tcp] as p5432
    [8000/tcp] as p8000
    [5173/tcp] as p5173
  }
}

rectangle "Docker Compose Runtime" as compose {
  database "postgres\n(postgres:16-alpine)" as postgres
  [backend\n(python:3.12-slim + uvicorn)] as backend
  [frontend\n(node:20-alpine + vite dev)] as frontend

  postgres <-down- backend : DATABASE_URL\npostgres:5432
  backend <-down- frontend : depends_on\nbackend
}

p5432 --> postgres : host:5432 -> container:5432
p8000 --> backend : host:8000 -> container:8000
p5173 --> frontend : host:5173 -> container:5173

note right of backend
Hardening (Compose/Dockerfile):
- runs as non-root user
- read_only filesystem
- /tmp as tmpfs
- cap_drop: ALL
- security_opt: no-new-privileges
Healthcheck:
- HTTP GET /api/v1/health/
end note

note right of frontend
Hardening (Compose/Dockerfile):
- runs as non-root user
- cap_drop: ALL
- security_opt: no-new-privileges
end note

note left of postgres
Hardening (Compose):
- security_opt: no-new-privileges
Healthcheck:
- pg_isready
end note

@enduml
